OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA chilly start will lead to a
OL,6,Ffine and dry day today, with plenty of
OL,7,Fsunshine. Skies may turn a little hazy
OL,8,Fthroughout the afternoon, but feeling
OL,9,Fwarm if not very warm in places.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA fine evening with some late
OL,12,Fsunshine. Overnight will remain dry
OL,13,Fwith further clear spells. A little
OL,14,Fchilly in the countryside but not as
OL,15,Fcold as recent nights.
OL,16,
OL,17,CWednesday:FAnother fine and dry day
OL,18,Fwith spells of sunshine, which again
OL,19,Fmaybe a little hazy at times. Feeling
OL,20,Fvery warm in the sunshine with light
OL,21,Fwinds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
